<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog | Occasus Lab</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Research-driven articles that feed directly into Occasus Lab's clarity tools. Powered by NotebookLM synthesis.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav__inner">
      <a class="nav__brand" href="index.html"><img src="assets/studio-occasus-logo.png" alt="Studio Occasus" height="36"></a>
      <nav class="nav__links"><a href="index.html#tools" class="nav__link">Tools</a><a href="index.html#pricing" class="nav__link">Pricing</a><a href="blog.html" class="nav__link active">Blog</a></nav>
      <a class="btn btn--sm btn--primary" href="index.html#tools">Try tools</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="blog-page">
    <section class="blog-hero">
      <span class="tag">The Occasus Lab Editorial</span>
      <h1>Research that builds better tools.</h1>
      <p>Every article follows the same loop: discover a scientific insight, translate it into a product rule, and publish it so the tools keep improving.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Pipeline explainer ────────────────────── -->
    <section class="blog-pipeline">
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <span class="flow__num">1</span>
        <h3>Academic Paper</h3>
        <p>Select peer-reviewed research on cognition, communication, or behavior.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="flow__arrow">&rarr;</span>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <span class="flow__num">2</span>
        <h3>NotebookLM Synthesis</h3>
        <p>Feed papers into a Google NotebookLM knowledge base for grounded Q&amp;A.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="flow__arrow">&rarr;</span>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <span class="flow__num">3</span>
        <h3>Editorial Article</h3>
        <p>Translate the synthesis into a 5-section article with product integration.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="flow__arrow">&rarr;</span>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <span class="flow__num">4</span>
        <h3>Tool Update</h3>
        <p>Each article generates new rules that improve the Clarity Rewriter and beyond.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Article Grid ──────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="blog-grid blog-grid--full">
      <a class="blog-card" href="cognitive-load-clarity.html">
        <span class="tag">Neuroscience</span>
        <h3>Cognitive Load and Why Clear Messaging Wins</h3>
        <p>A practical reading of cognitive load theory: what it means, why overloaded copy creates friction, and how product rules convert research into better communication.</p>
        <div class="blog-card__meta">
          <span>Article 01</span>
          <span>Feeds: Clarity Rewriter</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="blog-card" href="signal-noise-marketing.html">
        <span class="tag">Cybernetics</span>
        <h3>Signal vs. Noise: The Cybernetic Filter for Marketing</h3>
        <p>How cybernetics teaches us to amplify signal and dampen noise in every campaign layer — from headline to CTA.</p>
        <div class="blog-card__meta">
          <span>Article 02</span>
          <span>Feeds: Tone Analyzer</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <div class="blog-card blog-card--soon">
        <span class="tag">Behavioral Science</span>
        <h3>The Feedback Loop: How Usage Data Improves the Tools</h3>
        <p>A behind-the-scenes look at how Occasus Lab evolves from every rewrite, every headline scored, and every message generated.</p>
        <div class="blog-card__meta">
          <span>Coming soon</span>
          <span>Feeds: All tools</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── NotebookLM CTA ────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="cta-banner">
      <span class="tag">Powered by</span>
      <h2>Google NotebookLM</h2>
      <p>Our editorial pipeline uses NotebookLM to synthesize academic papers into grounded knowledge bases &mdash; ensuring every article stays citation-accurate and every tool rule is traceable to peer-reviewed research.</p>
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="https://notebooklm.google/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Explore NotebookLM &rarr;</a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer__inner">
      <div class="footer__brand"><img src="assets/studio-occasus-logo.png" alt="Studio Occasus" height="28"><p>Occasus Lab</p></div>
      <div class="footer__links"><a href="index.html">Home</a><a href="index.html#tools">Tools</a><a href="blog.html">Blog</a></div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
